(1077, '_transient_dash_29eefda0bdc5977617f778df7e755d87', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://it.wordpress.org/news/2016/01/meetup-brescia-27-gennaio-2016/''>Meetup Brescia: 27 gennaio 2016</a> <span class="rss-date">11 gennaio 2016</span><div class="rssSummary">Primo appuntamento del 2016 per il Meetup di Brescia presso il Parco Dell’Acqua, Largo Torrelunga, 7 (vicino a piazzale Arnaldo), mercoledì 27 gennaio a partire dalle 19:00. Agenda della serata: 19:00-19:30 – Chiacchiere di benvenuto 19:30-20:45 – Sono previsti diversi interventi: Come creare un child theme Alcuni consigli per migrare i siti WordPress su un nuovo server Alcune delle novità [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/wordpress-for-android-4-9-adds-fingerprint-scanner-improves-media-library''>WPTavern: WordPress for Android 4.9 Adds Fingerprint Scanner, Improves Media Library</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/wp-asset-clean-up-plugin-removes-unused-styles-and-scripts''>WPTavern: WP Asset Clean Up Plugin Removes Unused Styles and Scripts</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/buddypress-2-5-development-kicks-off-bp-api-dev-chat-begins-this-week''>WPTavern: BuddyPress 2.5 Development Kicks Off, BP-API Dev Chat Begins This Week</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Plugin popolare:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/siteorigin-panels/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Page Builder by SiteOrigin</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=siteorigin-panels&amp;_wpnonce=4d7a661e54&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Page Builder by SiteOrigin''>Installa</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no');
